2017-10-09|2017-10-15.description:
“MIND GAMES” part one! After reports of Sinestro’s return begin to spread, Hal Jordan travels to Earth looking to bring in his one-time Green Lantern partner. But a manhunt turns into a fight for his life as Hal must face the unmatchable power of the Man of Steel.

Continues the story from Superman #29 - A Minute Longer Part One.

On Mogo, in the Command Center, John Stewart gets an alert from Cyborg that something is happening on Earth, and the Green Lanterns would be best suited to deal with it. John then calls the other Earth Green Lanterns, and chooses Hal Jordan to deal with it, and sends Kyle and Guy out on Honor Guard Patrol. John then explains to Hal that Sinestro has been spotted on Earth, by none other then Superman.

When Hal gets to Earth he finds Superman who tells Hal that he was investigating some missing children when he was attacked by Parallax. Superman was then taken to the Antimatter Universe, but Superman escaped and steal Sinestro's ring and trap Parallax inside it.

Hal takes the ring, scans it and places it in a pocket dimension for safe keeping. He then offers to take Superman out for lunch but then Superman seems to be possessed by Parallax. The two heroes fight, Hal trying to get Parallax to release his friend and Possessed Superman trying to get Hal to realize his fears.

The fight comes to a abrupt stop when Superman is able to punch Hal so hard he stops attacking for a moment. Hal then realizes Superman is fine and it was him who was seeing things. Before Hal can figure out what happened he get a vision. Hector Hammond is in trouble and needs Hal to save him from the Krolotean Gremlins.
